name: INSPO FLOWERS - URCORNYVERSE
description: Development sketch for the character INSPO FLOWERS, part of the new upcoming URCORNYVERSE experience launching 01.10.21. Need some inspiration to create an NFT? Feeling stuck and bored with what you are creating? Look no further than the INSPO FLOWERS whose scent is perfect for kick starting that creative process and giving you ideas as to what you can do. INSPO FLOWERS are found randomly throughout the URCORNYVERSE and you know when you are near to one because you suddenly feel compelled to make something and tell people about it.
